m_q.target_metric: Maximum stadium capacity among venues used in the 2008-2009 Iran Pro League season
filters: 2008-2009 season (implicit from Past Season column referring to previous season)
sub_questions: What venues were used in the 2008-2009 season?
What is the capacity of each venue?
Which venue has the maximum capacity?

scale_issues: Capacity values contain commas as thousands separators (e.g., '35,000')
Capacity stored as string/object type but represents numeric values

format_notes: Capacity column contains comma-separated numeric values in quotes
Multiple teams may share the same venue
Past Season column indicates ranking or status from previous season

constraints: All teams in the dataset represent the 2008-2009 Iran Pro League season
Capacity must be converted from string to numeric for comparison
Need to handle duplicate venues when multiple teams share the same stadium
derived_filters: Remove duplicate venues to get unique venue-capacity pairs
output_format_requirements: Return the venue name with the highest capacity
May optionally include the capacity value for context
